Generelle Gliederung:

1. Business Understanding
  Determine Business Objectives, Assess Situation, Determining Analysis Goals, Project Plan

2. Data Understanding
  Collect Initial Data, Describe Data, Explore Data, Verify Data Quality

3. Data Preparation
  Select Data, Clean Data, Construct Data, Integrate Data, Format Data

4. Feature Engineering
  Feature Transformation, Feature Construction, Feature Selection, Feature Extraction

5. Data Mining Descriptive Modeling
  Business Reporting, Dashboards, Scorecards

6. Data Mining Predictive Modeling
  Data Mining, Text Mining, Forecasting

7. Decision Trees
  Decision Tree Learning, Random Forests, Gradient Boosting

8. Linear Regression
  Learning Process, Regularization

9. Artficial Neural Networks
  Overview

10.Association Analysis
  Association Rules, Association Rule Learning

11. Prescriptive Modeling
  Optimization and Simulation Overview

12. Evaluation
  Evaluate Results, Review Process, Determine next Steps


Inhalte einzelner Themen:

-> Statistics:
Mean, Variance, Median, Mode, Standard Deviation, Boxplot, Histogram, Skewness, Nominal Correlation Chi, Ordinal Correlation Pearsson

-> Preprocessing:
Outlier Detection: KNN Distance + Density Based

Missing Value Treatment: List Wise Deletion, Pair Wise Deletion, Variable Dropping, Mean/Mode/Median Imputation, Last Observation Carried Forward (LOCF), Next Observation Carried Backwards (NOCB), Linear Interpolation, Arbitrary Value Imputation, Missing Value Indicator, NA Category

Inbalenced Data Handling: Under-Sampling Tomek Links, Over-Sampling Smote

Feature Transformation: Discretization Euqal Witdh + Equal Frequency Binning, Feature Encoding Ordinal + One Hot + Target Encoding, Feature Scaling Normalization Min Max Scaling + Standardization Z-Score Scaling, Winsorization, Log Transformation

Feature Extraction: Principal Component Analysis (PCA)

Data Splitting: Train Test Validation Split, Cross Validation (CV)

-> Predictive Modeling:
Learning category: Supervised, Unsupervised, Reinforcement learning

Decision Tree: ID3 Information Gain, Random Forest Bootstrapping + Random Feature Selection, Gradient Boosting Sklearn

Linear Regression: Model Function, Ordinary Least Square (OLS), Root Mean Squared Error (RMSE), Under + Overfitting

Association Analysis: Support, Confidence, Lift, Apriori Algorithm

-> Evaluation:
RMSE, MAE, Confusion Matrix, Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-Score, Specificity
